modelVersions.name: NadiaNami
modelVersions.description:
Chibis in the style of Nada Namie

How to use
Doesn't need anything else than "chibi,1girl" to work, after that just add whatever else you want.

Misc
512 resolution trained on NAI without noise offset option for best LoRA compatibility.
Tested on NAI + AOM2. Personally I recommend NAI or other compatible models with good support for "watercolor","sketch","line drawing" and other medium tags.
AOM2 users might have to increase LoRA weight to around 1.2 and lower the default AOM2 negative weights to 1.0 weight to overcome the model default style.

All sample images are raw untouched txt2img.
